{"id":4218,"date":"2025-06-16T16:41:11","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:41:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4218"},"modified":"2025-06-16T16:41:11","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:41:11","slug":"kem-chong-nang-nang-tong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/kem-chong-nang-nang-tong\/","title":{"rendered":"Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u00f4ng GSC Triple Sun Block"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u00f4ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho m\u1ecdi l\u00e0n da &#8211; t\u1eeb da kh\u00f4, da d\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ebfn da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do GSC Triple Sun Block ra \u0111\u1eddi: gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n da &#8220;kh\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u&#8221; nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi-sao-ban-nen-chon-kem-chong-nang-gsc-triple-sun-block\"><\/span><b>V\u00ec sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng GSC Triple Sun Block?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-bao-ve-kep-%e2%80%93-vat-ly-ket-hop-hoa-hoc-hien-dai\"><\/span><b><i>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u00e9p &#8211; V\u1eadt l\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da ch\u1ec9 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, GSC Triple Sun Block t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 hai: m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u1eadt l\u00fd t\u1eeb Titanium Dioxide v\u00e0 Zinc Oxide t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tia UV, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 Tinosorb S gi\u00fap h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5, ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i tia UVA \u2013 UVB \u2013 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n su\u1ed1t 8 gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n thoa.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4219\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4219\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4219\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-1.webp\" alt=\"V\u00ec sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng GSC Triple Sun Block\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4219\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V\u00ec sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng GSC Triple Sun Block<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-gsc-triple-sun-block\"><\/span><b><i>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a GSC Triple Sun Block<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cao: SPF 50+ PA+++<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UVA, UVB v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm do \u00e1nh n\u1eafng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da nh\u1edd Niacinamide 2%<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean: b\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1, rau m\u00e1, hoa m\u1eabu \u0111\u01a1n, cam th\u1ea3o \u2013 v\u1eeba l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, v\u1eeba nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4220\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4220\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4220\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-2.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a GSC Triple Sun Block\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4220\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a GSC Triple Sun Block<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-diem-noi-bat-so-voi-cac-san-pham-khac\"><\/span><em><b>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c<\/b><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ed5 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ef1c r\u1ed9ng, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ea5t kem m\u1ecbn m\u01b0\u1ee3t, d\u1ec5 t\u00e1n, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ebft d\u00ednh, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eddn r\u00edt<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u00e0i l\u00e2u: Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thoa l\u1ea1i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">An to\u00e0n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da kh\u00f4, da d\u1ea7u \u2013 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eafng g\u1eaft v\u00e0 \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-noi-bat-%e2%80%93-duong-va-bao-ve-toan-dien\"><\/span><b>Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u2013 D\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4221\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4221\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4221\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-3.webp\" alt=\"Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4221\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t<\/b><\/td>\n<td><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng ch\u00ednh<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Titanium Dioxide, Zinc Oxide<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ecdc tia UVA, UVB, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Tinosorb S (Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol)<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UV to\u00e0n d\u1ea3i, c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Niacinamide 2%<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m n\u00e1m, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>B\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh da kh\u00f4 s\u1ea1m<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t hoa m\u1eabu \u0111\u01a1n, ho\u00e0ng c\u1ea7m, cam th\u1ea3o, rau m\u00e1<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-su-dung-dung-chuan-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4222\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4222\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4222\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-4.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/76-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea5y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kem kho\u1ea3ng 0.5g, ch\u1ea5m l\u00ean 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t: tr\u00e1n, m\u00e1, m\u0169i, c\u1eb1m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 t\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra n\u1eafng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 ph\u00fat.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi da \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam n\u1eb7ng, v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1edf ho\u1eb7c da qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u01b0 GSC Triple Sun Block. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, GSC ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &#8220;t\u1ea5m khi\u00ean v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc&#8221; cho l\u00e0n da b\u1ea1n trong m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GSC Triple Sun Block &#8211; gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n da &#8220;kh\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u&#8221; nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4224,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4218","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4218","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4218"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4218\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4225,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4218\/revisions\/4225"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4224"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4218"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4218"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4218"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}